works.description:
Batimat Gambia Limited, whose parent company is French, was founded in the year 2000 to bring together all the construction materials, household fittings and equipment under one roof specifically aimed at the construction industry and the local DIY market.

Product Range:
Its product range as well as it warehouse in Kanifing is impressive and vast indeed. Below are a few examples:

Air-conditioning, furniture for gardens, awnings, play-grounds, products and accessories, padlocks, locks and accessories, metallic roofs and walls, casings  for doors, windows and wood, iron, aluminium and PVC accessories.

Gypsum for ceiling, panels and coves, hydrometers, pumps and water tanks, waterproofing products and systems.

Thermal acoustic insulation, Venetian blinds and sunshades, pools fibre, concrete, heaters, products and accessories.

• Ceramic and porcelain tiles.

• PVC tubes, connections and panels.

• Wood, rubber and carpet linings.

• Security systems and products.

• Laminated parquets, panels and wainscots.

• Paints, varnishes and paint accessories

• Complete bathroom fixtures and fittings.

• Lumber.

• Steel re-enforcement rods
